 FOR SMELTER FUMES HAVE I BEEN NAMED,
    I AM AN EVIL POISONOUS SMOKE...
 BUT WHEN FROM POISON I AM FREED,
    THROUGH ART AND SLEIGHT OF HAND,
 THEN CAN I CURE BOTH MAN AND BEAST,
    FROM DIRE DISEASE OFTTIMES DIRECT THEM;
